1
00:00:02,170 --> 00:00:03,750
This is quite troublesome.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,460
Shiono-san?

3
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:14,720
Morimoto-san.

4
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,730
What's that supposed to mean?

5
00:00:17,730 --> 00:00:21,310
Making such a scene in public.

6
00:00:21,310 --> 00:00:22,980
Didn't I tell you?

7
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,400
I've thought about it.

8
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:28,360
How to protect Makoto.

9
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,920
Protecting my talent is my job.

10
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,320
This is none of your business.

11
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:35,120
Shiono-san, please wait.

12
00:00:36,450 --> 00:00:38,960
Please don't make decisions for me.

13
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:42,750
Makoto.

14
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:46,420
I thought you were a good model.

15
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,130
How disappointing.

16
00:00:50,180 --> 00:00:51,760
Can you even imagine?

17
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:56,850
No matter how many jobs you get,
they could all vanish in an instant.

18
00:00:57,850 --> 00:00:59,100
Do you know why?

19
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:00,440
That's...

20
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,270
Scandal.

21
00:01:02,850 --> 00:01:04,770
Over something as trivial as love.

22
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:06,860
Throwing away a bright future is just foolish.

23
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,740
Come on, let's go.

24
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:14,700
Shiono-san...

25
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,790
Would you be willing to work with me?
